EE200 ki quizzes se leke P2P ki quizzes tak tu to ha same rha pr maine pdhna chor diya(teri wajah se). YN singh k text ki Tshirt bnwaate hai :P.Thanks for making batti bearable for me. Love you man (and this feels so gay that I won't ever say that again atleast sober to nhi)
